    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve factors met or exceeded required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level 3 due to single-condition testing; this gap was reviewed and accepted because the single ASTM F1717 condition is directly representative of the COU and no extrapolation is required. All three QoIs satisfied pre-established acceptance criteria (QoI difference <10%, E/uval <1.96). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as sufficiently credible for the stated COU.",
